                <h1>How to Easily Change Your PS5 Background</h1>
                <p>To change your PS5 background, go to Settings > Personalization > Themes. You can select from pre-installed themes or choose "Custom" to upload your own image. Remember to choose images with a resolution of 1920x1080 for the best quality. Enjoy customizing your gaming experience with a personal touch!</p>
